IMAPStore astrophotography-proton-remote
   Port 1143
   Host 127.0.0.1
   User astrofotografie@protonmail.com
   PassCmd "gpg --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty --quiet --decrypt ~/.config/neomutt/crypt-store/astrophotography-proton"
   TLSType NONE

MaildirStore astrophotography-proton-local
   SubFolders Verbatim
   Path ~/.config/neomutt/astrophotography-proton/
   Inbox ~/.config/neomutt/astrophotography-proton/Inbox

Channel proton
   Far :astrophotography-proton-remote:
   Near :astrophotography-proton-local:
   Patterns * !Labels* !"All Mail"
   Create Both
   Expunge Both
   SyncState *

